PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1988-1206, which authorized the CANADIAN BROADCASTING CORPORATION to enter into an Agreement with Cadillac Fairview Corporation concerning the development of its BROADCASTING CENTRE in downtown Toronto, by revising certain particulars respecting the leasing of surrendered interests in the project.

precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1988-1206, which authorized the CANADIAN
BROADCASTING CORPORATION to enter into an Agreement with Cadillac Fairview
Corporation concerning the development of its BROADCASTING CENTRE in
downtown Toronto, by revising certain particulars respecting the leasing of
surrendered interests in the project.
